{
  "texts": [
    "We use Mistral 7B-Instruct (Jiang et al., 2023a) to examine whether the cited passages entail the generated sentence.",
    "BaselinesAs prior works use different setups and do not use LLMs, they are hard to compare directly.",
    "Instead, we use the following three LLM-based baselines.1.",
    "Direct Gen, a baseline that directly prompts the LLM to generate an outline, which is then used to generate the full-length article.2.",
    "RAG, a retrieval-augmented generation baseline that searches with the topic and uses the searched results together with the topic t to generate an outline or the entire article.3."
  ]
}